FLuka simulation tools

A) Producing geometry file:
 makeGeo -exp 12C_200 -run 1

B) Converting to shoe format:

 1) No region flag:
 - command:
 Txt2NtuRoot -in 12C_C_200_dat.txt -out 12C_C_200shoe.root -exp 12C_200 -run 1

 2) With region flag:
 - command:
Txt2NtuRoot -in 12C_C_200_dat.txt -out 12C_C_200shoereg.root -exp 12C_200 -run 1 -reg
